Package: waver
Type: Package
Title: Calculate Fetch and Wave Exposure
Version: 0.1.0
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.2),
    rgdal (>= 0.8),
    sp (>= 1.1)
Imports:
    geosphere (>= 1.4),
    rgeos (>= 0.3)
Authors@R: as.person(c(
        "Philippe Marchand <pmarchand@sesync.org> [aut, cre]",
        "David Gill [aut]"
    ))
Description: This package contains functions for calculating the
    fetch (length of open water distance along given directions)
    and estimating wave energy from wind and wave monitoring data.
